Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluffy, fluffy, fluffy, fluffy, fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yffulf, yffulf, yffulf, yffulf, yffulf...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now back to the right. Ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluffy, fluffy, fluffy, fluffy, fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Scarfs are warm, but they feel\Nso prickly on my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we do these fluffy exercises,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,let's not do them with the scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this stuff coming from your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm not quite sure, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Then I shall solve this mystery for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you're up to the task, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:01:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't test me! I got a hundred\Non my science test before!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho... Then I shall give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow... Now, Little. Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You go like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You must solve the mystery\Nin order to free your finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I'm gonna solve this in a jiffy\Nand get rid of this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Yachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who is this Yachi you speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcoming the New Year by studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:02:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I become such an honor student?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Are you awake?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Are you awake?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah, I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Can I call you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Sure, you can call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare for you to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, was this some kind of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...wanted to give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you watching TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what kind of answer is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This year's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing anything for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We basically just go to my grandparents' place\Nfor a bit, but that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get New Year's money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I guess I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura? Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I was just remembering your thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! M-My thighs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, really? I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Well, you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That wasn't sexual harassment.\NThat was a totally normal thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why my thighs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking how nice\Nyour lap pillow was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, because I'm lying down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you prefer me\Nto make them harder or softer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My thighs. Which would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're fine just the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best not to gain weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably worry about\Nnot losing too much weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I'm drinking that tea. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...using that thing all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we do New Year greetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep hanging out this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Goodnight" sounds nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Sounds nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she just want to wish me a Happy New Year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to be like, your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be too hard. I mean,\NI don't have that many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I sorta really want to be that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I told her she already was,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it'd make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even if the phrase "best friend"\Nmay sound the same when we say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there might be a difference in our\Nactual definition of the phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The level that Adachi wants\Nto take this relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was so impossibly high that I'd probably\Nneed to sprout wings to even attain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to work harder this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that and then immediately do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:08:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think how I feel about Shimamura's chest\Nwill basically determine things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly I want from Shimamura
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,should be determined there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I want to see Shimamura's chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... I can't say I don't want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't say I'd particularly\Npursue this venture, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, so it's pretty normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My feelings for Shimamura are pure,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I like Shimamura as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I love "Goodnight."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be an issue if I dove\Ninto Shimamura's bosom right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm completely normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Her face? Her chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, wait... That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:10:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what they mean by the biter gets bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think "digging my own grave"\Nis more fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't separate my struggles\Nfrom Shimamura just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that my dye job was beginning to fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"2/4 (Tues)"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's now February.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Winter break had ended,\Nwe got new seating assignments,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was finally getting used to\Nsaid seating assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,January was over in a blink of an eye,\Nand now it's February.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, Adachi seems to be acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Adachi's always acting weird, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When our eyes meet, she looks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to ask if she wants to hang out\Nand she ends up running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that these past few days,\NI haven't even heard her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she have to be such a troublemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey. Hey, yo, Shima! I'm Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't Hawaii and winter break\Nended a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't actually need anything. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she throwing that thing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would I be talking about?\NYou know, the boomerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Yeah, I'm sure, uh,\Nmy little sister is throwing it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her I challenge her to a duel\Nonce she gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere far away... Wait, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you wanted to\Nstop by someplace after school...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we don't have to if you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm so insanely busy today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Of course, I'm not busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to rub that in, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lying when I said I was busy.\NSo let's go somewhere. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you have somewhere in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not anywhere exact, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"But"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... I think I want some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So Miss Adachi would like some sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yup... Snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you prefer something not sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, er... Something sweet is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my hand. Here. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're going to have something sweet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a donut shop right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you prefer Japanese sweets, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant. I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have somewhere in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I dye my hair again or go back to black?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure because I've never\Nseen you with black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am the purest little\NSnow White you'll find.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. My hair's starting to grow out,\Nso I was wondering what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What about here? We can get takeout\Nand eat on the bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Heart {\i1}Chocolat{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Valentine's Day Fair"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I try lifting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lifting what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm floating! I'm floating! Wait... Ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, my armpits hurt! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were heavier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, how rude can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I just figured I could lift you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you want chocolate this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I love sweet things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty. I guess I'll buy you\Nsomething again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Valentine's Day Fair"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Valentine's... It says Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I... guess it's that time of year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Valentine's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not... a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Adachi bring me here just to\Nshow me this Valentine's poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I guess I should just say that was\Na rather roundabout way of doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans on the 14th, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you don't, could we hang out\Non the 14th, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Do you want chocolate or do you\Nwant to give me chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I mean, either. Or rather, let's exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure Hino and Nagafuji\Ndo something like that every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't see this going\Nas smoothly as it'd go for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been doing this for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't the point to give someone chocolate\Nsuddenly that day as a surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many years I'll be around Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe just until graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, once we move up a year,\Nwe might end up in different classes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and that might be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:19:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's actually some hope\Nknowing it might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There're still plenty of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi was trying to take a step out\Nof the flow of our day-to-day life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that whatever direction she's taking,\Nit's always facing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't help but admire\Nher determination and resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Let's do Valentine's Day this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, every day just seemed grey and endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But on this day, February 4th,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next ten days of grey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed to slowly have color added to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Getting side dishes for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, today, I'll get...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.73,0:22:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's me! It's been forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You sorta became really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Was "sorta" necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get your number?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji had witnessed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Much lower key than a housewife\Nwitnessing something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.19,0:23:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a call when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 7: 'Please Choose\Nthe Best Chocolate for Me'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 7: 'Please Choose\Nthe Best Chocolate for Me'"\N"Tarumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Nagafuji in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, check it out! Hino here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.65,0:23:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You went overseas for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:24:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Had to get the ol' chocolate-covered\Nmacadamia nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.85,0:24:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit your complainin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
